    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《按钮效应》是一款短小简约的第一人称解谜游戏，其中每个按钮都有存在的意义。走进晦涩的博物馆，探究隐蔽的联系，获得有关空间的思考……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299940/extras/d72a1e9687f4814fe2a81576952c353e.poster.avif?t=1770967593\" width=580 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299940/extras/d72a1e9687f4814fe2a81576952c353e.webm?t=1770967593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299940/extras/d72a1e9687f4814fe2a81576952c353e.mp4?t=1770967593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299940/extras/35e7206ce7660f9444069ae7f0cd6b35.webp?t=1770967593\" width=614 height=32 /></span><br>挑战自我，仔细观察、理解自己行动的结果，了解馆内的展品。你的每一步和每一个解法都有可能让你知道新的东西。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299940/extras/5ccee923dbafe8211f8522ea98ff8242.poster.avif?t=1770967593\" width=580 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299940/extras/5ccee923dbafe8211f8522ea98ff8242.webm?t=1770967593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299940/extras/5ccee923dbafe8211f8522ea98ff8242.mp4?t=1770967593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299940/extras/2a4fcff27579240427db938c5ce4ea29.webp?t=1770967593\" width=614 height=32 /></span><br>打开新的房门，进入纵横交错的空间，感受建筑内部运转的奇妙。平心静气，体悟这里的静谧，从容参观。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299940/extras/b306dc0644625e5386900e05f63997ad.poster.avif?t=1770967593\" width=580 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299940/extras/b306dc0644625e5386900e05f63997ad.webm?t=1770967593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299940/extras/b306dc0644625e5386900e05f63997ad.mp4?t=1770967593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299940/extras/3327d5071bdbbc744d370afcdc46690c.webp?t=1770967593\" width=614 height=32 /></span><br>留心细微之处，见证每一个变化。怀有好奇之心，就能揭示一切事物之间有意义的联系，获得更多理解和思考。秘密就在眼前，等你发现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299940/extras/e3f7183f66deb2b2c37db268d52c958e.webp?t=1770967593\" width=600 height=5 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >展品就是谜题，彼此紧密联系，让你有所体悟，也激发你的好奇。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同房间相连交错，等待你解锁与探索</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >剧情碎片等待你收集，集齐就能看到真正的结局</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >内部场景氛围宁静，搭配悦耳的钢琴曲</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操作简单，容易上手</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以选择安静模式（关闭配音）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提示系统以游戏的形式展现</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299940/extras/e3f7183f66deb2b2c37db268d52c958e.webp?t=1770967593\" width=600 height=5 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>注意：这款游戏由单人开发者独立开发，流程较短，总计3到4小时。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299940/extras/e3f7183f66deb2b2c37db268d52c958e.webp?t=1770967593\" width=600 height=5 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
